import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { IEmployee } from 'src/Shared/Interfaces/IEmployee'; import { EmployeeServiceService } from 'src/Shared/Services/employee-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'], }) export class AppComponent { title = 'Corelia'; AllEmployee: IEmployee[] = []; constructor(private employeeServiceService: EmployeeServiceService) {} ngOnInit() { this.employeeServiceService.GetAll().subscribe((data) => { this.AllEmployee.push(data); console.log(this.AllEmployee); }); } }
